@NODE REQUIRED "What you need to run Hexen"
@SMARTWRAP
@{b}Requirements@{ub}


You'll need the following to be able to start Hexen:@{LINE}


·@{LINDENT 2} 68020+ (68040+ recommended)
@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}
·@{LINDENT 2} AGA, CyberGraphX or Picasso96
@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}
·@{LINDENT 2} AmigaOS 3.0
@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}
·@{LINDENT 2} about 8MB FastRAM
@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}
·@{LINDENT 2} PC Hexen I V1.0+ commercial or demo ".wad"
@{LINDENT 0}@{PAR}


That's it.@{LINE}

@ENDNODE
